{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/punc/punc-03450/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PUNC-03450"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:34:50"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Punch-Drunk Love"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld, pan, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["high key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Two women walk into a warehouse."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PUNC-03450","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PUNC-03450"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/canvas/1/3bbfb6ca-4935-4e5b-b9c4-7f7d1460083e","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2025-08-19T20:04:00.336Z","creator":"Olivia Flores","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Lena’s name speaks: it means \"light,\" but she is also “lenient” when it comes to Barry’s strange behavior, and she “leans” into Barry to push their relationship forward.</p>"}],"target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/canvas/1#xywh=1110,199,372,353"},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/canvas/1/d03ebfee-51ba-4121-a907-b322d694fd49","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2025-08-19T20:04:31.288Z","creator":"Olivia Flores","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This two-shot portrays&nbsp;opposite perspectives and attitudes through these two women in Barry's life:&nbsp;his sister's disapproval and her muttering of, \"He's wearing that goddamn suit again, I don't know why she is wearing that suit, he doesn't usually dress like that\" contrasts with Lena's caring interest and more subdued, \"That's fine.\" Their clothing also signifies this tension: his sister is dressed in darker purples while Lena in wearing a lighter, more vibrant hue of this color (purple is a mix of blue and red, Barry's and Lena's main colors throughout the film, so the mix here is significant). His sister's neckline suggests she is closed off, while Lena's unbuttoned neckline conveys her openness. Lena's taller body and position in the frame show she occupies a higher moral ground than Barry's disapproving sister.</p>"}],"target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/punc/punc-03450/canvas/1#xywh=148,312,1440,485"}]}]}]}